This paper proposes a novel approach for using unsupervised boosting to create an ensemble of generative models. The paper discusses the effectiveness of the approach on density estimation, classification, and sample generation on benchmark datasets for a wide range of generative models. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.SD (Sound).
